profile:
Categories: Carpet & Rug Retailers, Floor Retailers

Carpets & Home. If you or one of your friends are interested in flooring for your home or office, we invite you to visit us and see Saskatoon’s largest selection of Hand Made Rugs, modern and traditional Area Rugs, Hardwood, Laminate, Carpet, Vinyl, Tile, Luxury Vinyl Tile (LVT) and more...
We’d enjoy meeting you and demonstrating our commitment to service, selection, quality and fair pricing.

Services
We are pleased to offer:

    - Installation of Hardwood, Laminate, Tile, Broadloom, and Vinyl flooring
    - In Home shopping and display
    - Free delivery
    - Cleaning and Repair of all area rugs to the highest standards
    - Area rug appraisals for Insurance purposes and peace of mind
    - Carpet Search: we will find you the Area Rug that is perfect for your
      home if we don’t already have it in our large selection

profile:
Habitat for Humanity Saskaton’s ReStore sells new and gently used home improvement products and supplies.

Everything sold in the ReStore has been donated by companies and individuals who want to help Habitat for Humanity meet its goal of eliminating poverty housing in Saskatoon. That is how we are able to sell everything for substantially less than retail.  We constantly receive new inventory from a variety of generous supporters, so every trip to the ReStore offers a unique opportunity to discover a fantastic deal, a one-of-a-kind gem or the missing item in your otherwise perfect design.
